{"tid":1484532,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"到底留守緊既人 知唔知我地主線係咩？","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:28:56.000Z","uid":125566,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c25fcdd864e2b517b2deee95ffc7ed8a60fafe25","tid":1484532,"uid":125566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"撒回送中條例係我地主線！<br />\n警民衝突係主線衍生出黎既支線！<br />\n可唔可以唔好變到每一次都靜係想撚班狗呢？<br />\n係咪放一放催淚彈 跟著無人比狗拉 就代表你地贏啦？係人都知宜家班狗濫用警權 根本已經唔差呢一晚 <br />\n比你地今晚撚到班狗 跟著聽日所有新聞既焦點就變到示威者再次留守 狗放催淚彈驅散  而170萬人上街變成次要 咁你地就開心 滿足？<br />\n希望留守既人睇完 可以乖乖地番左屋企先！"},{"pid":"8fe583972f255eb812647040ae73601e0f954b15","tid":1484532,"uid":125566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:28.000Z","msg":"幫手推比留守既人見到"},{"pid":"3c3fc3318d5d7d16006231ab0c72ae15f2859af3","tid":1484532,"uid":125566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4d0dd8f792f7e7db2370c639e2dd8d60dbce272","tid":1484532,"uid":125566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4964288a0495b95c9c44786fa0b600a2a14f8762","tid":1484532,"uid":125566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"全世界 番屋企"},{"pid":"2ac5877b6317cd26438ea8531767a8bc370d96f9","tid":1484532,"uid":289974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788faffe9367c06f5a736f2811132460e8e7392e","tid":1484532,"uid":125566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"全世 番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a72cfc02ef963bc5d1641a333fc801db2163a3d","tid":1484532,"uid":247896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"返屋企<img src=\"/